cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about improving object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves developing a new loss function, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using interior-point methods, which is a technique commonly used in optimization and numerical analysis (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on the COCO dataset, which is a popular benchmark in multimedia (cs.MM).
